## RR Day 37 — sed, Stream Editor

### Completed
- Substituted text in a stream:
  echo "the server is down" | sed 's/down/up/'
- Substituted across a real file without modifying it:
  sed 's/nologin/DISABLED/' /etc/passwd | head -10
